# .agents-workspace/

# Generated sample apps/ and packages/ (from `usm init` in single-package mode)
# These are NOT generated in normal use — `usm init` creates usmconfig.json.
# If they appear, it's from a stale run.
apps/
packages/

# Generated AGENTS.md (regenerated by `usm generate`)
# (uncomment to commit generated AGENTS.md)
# AGENTS.md

